Invocation Name: common knowledge test
des:
Common knowledge is a game that asks those practical, every day questions everyone should know. but do you?

Test your Common knowledge in fun categories like Chemistry, General knowledge, Common Sense and much, much more. For example
Which of these combination of colors can be used to make green color?
A) Blue and yellow
B) Red and yellow
C) Blue and orange
..the answer is Blue and yellow! To make green color, just add blue and yellow colors in equal proportion

Just say "Alexa, open Common Knowledge Test" to take the test.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
